# =============================================================================
# Local development build artifacts
# Produced by: make local / make dev, ./scripts/build-local.sh,
#              cmake -B build ., go build, and the harness.
#
# These must never be committed. The script + Makefile + .gitignore
# combination guarantees this for quick iteration on gRPC / feature branches.
# =============================================================================
